---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Scroll-Out
---
<p>Scroll to see CSS variables applied via Scroll-Out.</p>
<div data-scroll class="panel">I move based on --scroll-percent</div>

{% block head %}
<style>
  .panel { height: 200vh; display: grid; place-items: center; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 12px; }
  [data-scroll] { transform: translateY(calc(var(--scroll-percent, 0) * 1px)); transition: transform .1s linear; }
</style>
{% endblock %}

{% block scripts %}
<script src="https://unpkg.com/scroll-out/dist/scroll-out.min.js"></script>
<script>ScrollOut();</script>
{% endblock %}
